l-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Oyp96n.gif&h=a744baa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7faf47c09d800daa66cff8282fdc5aa8c30676a2","tid":1154050,"uid":230104,"like":119,"dislike":4,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"油麻地碧街41號4樓一間賓館，凌晨2時許，一名姓黃女子（34歲）與男友因感情問題爭執，對方拂袖離開，女事主情緒激動，從窗口攀出外牆危站簷篷上，企圖跳樓。<br />\n<br />\n消防員接報到場張開氣墊，西九龍衝鋒隊警員在場游說，約40分鐘後，將她勸服，返回屋內。<br />\n<br />\n女事主手腳有傷痕，不排除曾被人虐打，由救護員送院治理。西九龍衝鋒隊員事後稱，主要是動之以情，耐心勸解。警方將案件列傷人案處理。據悉，女事主早年在新西蘭留學後回港。"},{"pid":"5729d16b741cde31b114ff43549b57c8cb150211","tid":1154050,"uid":99700,"like":312,"dislike":7,"score":305,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/qy3fxoa2lyh11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fqy3fxoa2lyh11.jpg&h=35f4c270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMr stark i feel so good"},{"pid":"eec737834b66afaa940139717fe6b2f82fd5e799","tid":1154050,"uid":7673,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"咁樣踩住個華字都無跌落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a8ee7cbbab7ad267039a1f27bdb7800b4ef6f1","tid":1154050,"uid":3189,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"啲圖好有潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84e10c3d33782983a16c2893d192d62f5e9f0c1","tid":1154050,"uid":71579,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"marvel仲請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9f04ff204e908d34b49a17f64d35200736f92c","tid":1154050,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe44ea567459f261aa2ffe2b563edf5009b16bc3","tid":1154050,"uid":86686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ce9b572668f38ff810cd8683d908c0df72034